The Art of Living Foundation is hosting a panel discussion under the Meditate Africa Series that focuses on socio-economic matters facing the African continent in the time of COVID-19. The panel discussion with Gurudev Sri Sri Ravi Shankar is under the theme of Africa Innovates the role of meditation in driving innovation in education, health and commerce. For more news, visit sabcnews.com and also #SABCNews, #Coronavirus, #COVID19 on Social Media.  